# Windsurf Rules — Blockchain Agent Skills

Read AGENTS.md before any blockchain operation.

## Policy

1. Load using-blockchain-agent-skills for routing
2. Simulate before broadcast — always
3. Never log or return private keys
4. Block OFAC-sanctioned addresses
5. One primary skill per operation thread

## Lifecycle

/plan → /simulate → /confirm → /broadcast → /confirm-depth

Copy to `.windsurfrules` or install via VS Code extension.
